data.description: Charming home near Downtown OKC. Located in a prime location, just 1 mile from OU Health Science Center, this cute updated 4 bedroom home would be the perfect investment opportunity! It is located just minutes from Midtown, Uptown, the Arts District and the Bricktown Entertainment District. The kitchen is fully remodeled with new modern countertops and a beautiful white hexagon backsplash, as well as a new stainless-steel microwave and dishwasher. This home also has a new HVAC system, hot water tank and the water service line was recently replaced as well. Don't miss this chance to own a move-in ready home close to all the downtown action!
